{"tid":83020,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"未來會推岀自家品牌既產品，應如何防偽","createTime":"2017-01-16T11:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T14:47:17.000Z","uid":53331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0decd35804822fb96d2d36db177d7711edb06bf9","tid":83020,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:47:27.000Z","msg":"想問下應該點樣去保障自己產品比人抄襲都可以有法律保障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。商標註冊其實係咪唔可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲人換個商標就冇事。。件產品唔似冇嘴貓咁統一全部用冇嘴貓設計。所以唔能夠為單一圖像做註冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320f20afb9dc3e69cf622a8ee7444521944fdf41","tid":83020,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:00:48.000Z","msg":"首先要註冊啦<br />\n人地要抄你都防唔到<br />\n你係做得好先會有人抄<br />\n到時咪同條例解決"},{"pid":"b6dcd68ca5f738083bae0aeca66328cbdecacf2d","tid":83020,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:28:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先要註冊啦<br />\n人地要抄你都防唔到<br />\n你係做得好先會有人抄<br />\n到時咪同條例解決</blockquote><br />\n你係指註冊商標？ 註冊商標剩係保護到個logo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似冇咩意義"},{"pid":"d2d444d31741875b7222c81b8188956adde601d6","tid":83020,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:32:17.000Z","msg":"上網問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問專門做知識產權既律師啦"},{"pid":"cd2c360f4a180071176b7cd91f82e24013b59de1","tid":83020,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:34:17.000Z","msg":"商標註冊好簡單, 比得起錢就可以<br />\n你想將自家品牌既產品註冊, 保障自已利益<br />\n呢樣就複雜好多, 涉及好多技術問題<br />\n你 google 下相關既公司, 佢地有幫人搞的"},{"pid":"dc9ca2a928b3288e5d959e99ad80a29319e335fd","tid":83020,"uid":66091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T12:38:11.000Z","msg":"自己做埋抄襲個個<br />\n正版翻版通吃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6776446cb2c8f3dd6835236d149b5a29d06b7314","tid":83020,"uid":75594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:47:17.000Z","msg":"註冊商標之外仲可以為產品註冊版權，咁啲個樣一模一樣，但商標唔同嘅商品一樣告得入。就似政府力推嘅二次創作都會俾人告，因為入面有版權。"}]}